other "friends" can grab the most.

62
00:04:55,792 --> 00:04:57,917
What is a genius?

63
00:04:58,708 --> 00:05:00,375
A natural talent.

64
00:05:01,833 --> 00:05:03,643
At five, I had read
through all the classics,

65
