73
00:05:20,750 --> 00:05:22,351
So, Mr. Prodigy...

74
00:05:22,375 --> 00:05:22,917
Genius.

75
00:05:23,292 --> 00:05:24,227
Mr. Genius.

76
00:05:24,251 --> 00:05:26,375
