94
00:06:02,083 --> 00:06:04,059
There's still some water
from the melted ice.

95
00:06:04,083 --> 00:06:05,208
Let's check this out.

96
00:06:10,208 --> 00:06:11,333
Tie him up.

97
00:06:11,792 --> 00:06:12,792
Money! Money!

98
00:06:12,875 --> 00:06:13,976
Qin, you've improved.

99
