234
00:10:07,583 --> 00:10:08,375
Let's talk about our case.

235
00:10:08,417 --> 00:10:09,417
Just did.

236
00:10:09,583 --> 00:10:10,583
Did what?

237
00:10:10,625 --> 00:10:12,393
Told you everything.

238
00:10:12,417 --> 00:10:13,851
Our boss will

239
00:10:13,875 --> 00:10:14,875
